reviewText: MY KIDS HAV BEEN WATCHING THIS TAPE FOR OVER A YEAR, IT IS THE BEST BABYSITTER WE EVER HAD! I CAN'T GET THEIR ATTENTION WHEN BARNEY IS ON. IT'S LIKE I DON'T EXIST. SIGNED.......THEIR DAD.
in good shape
Kids love it
I was extremely pleased with this product and delivery time.  I was so glad you were able to accommodate with the find of Barney Live! in New York City.

Okay, when I was little I adored this movie to no end. I've been looking everywhere to get it at a reasonable price so that one day I could show my kids or little cousins what I used to watch when I was younger. And sometimes it's just nice to remanence in the old days. Thanks so much!!!
I have 3 children and all have enjoyed Barney Live in New York City.  Great songs and dancing.  I even liked this one.

I am a Mamaw that just learned about this wonderful purple dinosaur from my grandson.
Jake is 3 1/2 and adores Barney....has learned all of his songs, and this video is one of his favorites.  It shows him how nice and loving Barney is to all people.
I recently took Jake to see Barney in a Colorful Stage Show, and because of this wonderful video it helped him make the connection to the real Barney!!
I find myself sitting down with him to watch, and now I know all the songs too!!
Please...take the time to enjoy Barney, and friends with the little ones...this is the perfect video to help you get in the mood!!

There is a lot of singing and dancing (all the old Barney favorites). But the best part is seeing the children in the auidence who are obviously enjoying the musical. My son dances with them, laughs with them and even shouts with them (when asked to by Barney). It is like being there (Radio City Music Hall) without having to stand in line to get into the theater!

My 2-year-old boy loves this video very much. Actually, all of my family loves it. The songs are beautiful, and it has a story in it. We also have  the video titled "Barney goes to school", "Barney's  songs", and "Barney's musical scrapbook". What I have found  is that Barney's home videos give children fun, imagination, and education.  Barney shares everything with children; He plays, dances, sings, and  studies, and more... So, get it and enjoy it! This is the one you shouldn't  miss!
Thank Barney and his friends.

This video captures all the excitement of Barney's live stage show, and includes a wide assortment of creatively presented children's songs. My two-year-old daughter really loves this video. In addition to Barney and  his friends, kids will also be amused by the Winkster, who is a clever,  leprochaun-like character with a funny voice and dance (he steals the  Barney Bag!). Other favorite scenes include a dancing baby elephant, a cute  little bird hatching out of an egg, and several silly "monkeys"  jumping on a bed. Older kids like this one too (my 4-year-old niece and my  6-year-old and 8-year-old nephews enjoy it).
This video is filled with everything you could want from Barney - music, humor, and of course, love and learning for all kids!

Barney Live! In New York City is by far the best Barney ever.  It was my daughters favorite as a child, she was 2 when she got it.  She would act out the different parts. (Baby Bops blanket stuck under the bar bell)  I still have the original tape from 1997.  Wish they would re-release it on DVD.  It does not disappoint. The songs they do on this episode are great.  I know Barney gets on many peoples nerves but these shows are not for you, the adult, they are for the children, and they enjoy them immensely.
good condition
I WOULD RECOMMEND-GREAT
